{"id": 2909, "genre": 1001, "title": "你觉得新时代的“情商高”应该是啥样子的？", "description": "来说说现如今你都是怎么理解“情商”这个词，以及，你觉得哪些说法可能属于对“情商”的误会。（题图来自：iStock ©️ lankogal）", "record_count": 4990, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190422162533vlJ5ZOTA6UR08fCk.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-04-23T03:00:36Z", "options": [{"id": 340736, "content": "不随便看别人的手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1622567}, {"id": 340737, "content": "记住别人的难处，不揭人伤疤。比如朋友父亲去世，就别在他面前老提自己爸爸多好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1598499}, {"id": 340738, "content": "能够换位思考，理解并尊重别人的不同。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1644094}, {"id": 340739, "content": "能够让他人以及自己在某些情况下舒服。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1446744}, {"id": 349187, "content": "让人相处的很舒服", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1670019}, {"id": 340740, "content": "情商是让别人舒服，智商是让自己舒服。双商在线，是在别人和自我之间的平衡。", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1596218}, {"id": 342532, "content": "不标榜自己高情商，不揭穿不会聊天还硬聊的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1415407}, {"id": 340742, "content": "满地都是6便士，我却抬头看到了月亮", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1644105}, {"id": 340743, "content": "同意下面那位朋友说的，感觉现在很多人都把情商直接等于成了圆滑。", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 806190}, {"id": 340744, "content": "明知领导在胡扯，还要拍手称快", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 585058}, {"id": 340745, "content": "不会让对方太难堪", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1480324}, {"id": 340746, "content": "这，看峰哥直播呀", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 930426}, {"id": 340747, "content": "不世故圆滑，考虑对人感受，尊重每个人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1518100}, {"id": 341003, "content": "让人舒服，想和他呆在一起", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1537751}, {"id": 340749, "content": "能够理解没有同等资源的穷人对于城市规则的陌生和轻度违反。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1308727}, {"id": 340750, "content": "在抄别人答案的时候，不问对不对，确定不之类的？", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1644115}, {"id": 341007, "content": "孔子所说的中庸", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1117871}, {"id": 340752, "content": "你们说的情商，其实是教养", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 923945}, {"id": 340753, "content": "真诚对人，换位思考", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1644122}, {"id": 340754, "content": "与人为善，和而不同，防人之心不可无", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1644124}, {"id": 340755, "content": "看破不说破", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1641558}, {"id": 340756, "content": "理解包容，有批判性思维，不恭维，不刻意讨好，但办事本分有担当，", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1644133}, {"id": 341012, "content": "见人说人话 见鬼说鬼话，但人和鬼都不讨厌", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 719815}, {"id": 340757, "content": "于人于己都舒服。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1438577}, {"id": 340758, "content": "与人相处不勉强自己同时让别人舒服", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1256841}, {"id": 340759, "content": "不总是想当年", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1644151}, {"id": 340760, "content": "学会欣赏形形色色的人与物，不以对错评判世界。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1450924}, {"id": 340761, "content": "自己最失控的时候仍然温柔以待身边一人一物", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1644156}, {"id": 340762, "content": "世界上本没有EQ，近几十年才冒出来的新词儿。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1449854}, {"id": 340763, "content": "敬而不失，与人恭而有礼，四海之内，皆兄弟也。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1617566}, {"id": 341019, "content": "很懂得看脸色，不随意介入别人的聊天", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1633464}, {"id": 342043, "content": "让人觉得和ta待在一起很舒服", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1602649}, {"id": 340764, "content": "懂得倾听，说出来的话让大家都舒服", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 202602}, {"id": 340765, "content": "有自己的意见，也能容纳倾听别人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1644169}, {"id": 340767, "content": "追到喜欢的女孩子", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 961264}, {"id": 341023, "content": "批评你但是让你觉得很舒服", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1438133}, {"id": 340768, "content": "能够在适当的时候换位思考", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1644174}, {"id": 341025, "content": "能心安理得的得过且过", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1619326}, {"id": 340771, "content": "考虑问题比较周到，让对方感到舒服和放松，愿意与之相处，不无趣。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1644178}, {"id": 340772, "content": "幽默 有趣", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1405090}, {"id": 341284, "content": "幽默而不烂俗…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1604142}, {"id": 340773, "content": "双赢", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1466756}, {"id": 340774, "content": "有就事论事的能力，时刻保持着从容，并拥有自律性。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1393417}, {"id": 340775, "content": "开心自己，尊重他人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1644186}, {"id": 340776, "content": "自尊且从容的活着并让愿意与你相处的人舒服愉悦", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1464711}, {"id": 341032, "content": "不抹杀自我，也多少成全别人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1020584}, {"id": 340777, "content": "自嘲", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1632846}, {"id": 340778, "content": "沟通时让人感到舒服，考虑别人的感受。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1621385}, {"id": 340779, "content": "学会闭嘴", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1618016}, {"id": 340780, "content": "一定一定不要伤人的自尊心", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1644191}]}